---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Contact Sula Catering Vancouver | Request a Custom Catering Quote"
	description="Contact Sula Catering for Indian wedding, corporate, and private party catering across Vancouver. Call 604-215-1130 or request a custom quote online."
	canonical="/contact"
>

	<Fragment slot="schema">
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org","@type": "ContactPage",
			"name": "Contact Sula Catering Vancouver",
			"description": "Contact information and quote request for Sula Catering Vancouver.",
			"mainEntity": {"@id": "https://sulacatering.com/#organization"}
		})} />
	</Fragment>

	<section class="hero" style="min-height:60vh;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.6) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 100%), url('https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<p class="gold-label">Begin the Conversation</p>
			<h1>Let's Plan<br/><em>Your Event</em></h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">Tell us about your celebration. We'll respond within 24 hours with a custom menu and quote.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/request-a-quote/" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">Three Ways to Reach Us</p>
				<h2>Always <em>Listening</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
				<p>Whether it's a quick question, a last-minute booking, or a fully custom <a href="/weddings" style="color:var(--gold);border-bottom:1px solid var(--gold)">wedding menu</a> — we're here. Most quote requests are answered within 24 hours.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="contact-cards">
				<div class="contact-card reveal">
					<div class="icon">✆</div>
					<h3>Call Us</h3>
					<p>Speak directly with our catering coordinator for any question, big or small.</p>
					<a href="tel:6042151130">604-215-1130</a>
				</div>
				<div class="contact-card reveal delay-100">
					<div class="icon">✉</div>
					<h3>Email Us</h3>
					<p>Send your event details, menu preferences, and timeline — we'll get back to you fast.</p>
					<a href="mailto:catering@sulaindianrestaurant.com">catering@sulaindianrestaurant.com</a>
				</div>
				<div class="contact-card reveal delay-200">
					<div class="icon">◆</div>
					<h3>Quote Request</h3>
					<p>Use our online form to share your event details and receive a custom quote within 24 hours.</p>
					<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/request-a-quote/">Request a Quote →</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-plum">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">Visit Sula</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Our <em>Locations</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
				<p style="max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;font-size:16px;color:rgba(245,237,224,0.85)">Four locations across Vancouver. Visit us in-restaurant or come say hello at the Café.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="locations-grid">
				<div class="location-card reveal">
					<h3>Commercial Drive</h3>
					<p class="addr">1128 Commercial Drive<br/>Vancouver, BC</p>
					<p class="phone">604-215-1130</p>
				</div>
				<div class="location-card reveal delay-100">
					<h3>Davie Street</h3>
					<p class="addr">1708 Davie Street<br/>Vancouver, BC</p>
					<p class="phone">604-428-4400</p>
				</div>
				<div class="location-card reveal delay-200">
					<h3>Main Street</h3>
					<p class="addr">4172 Main Street<br/>Vancouver, BC</p>
					<p class="phone">604-874-5375</p>
				</div>
				<div class="location-card reveal delay-300">
					<h3>Sula Café</h3>
					<p class="addr">260 East 5th Ave<br/>Vancouver, BC</p>
					<p class="phone">778-386-1130</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- INTERNAL LINKS -->
	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">Browse Our Services</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Explore <em>Sula Catering</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="related-links">
				<a href="/weddings" class="related-link reveal">
					<p class="meta">Service · Wedding Catering</p>
					<h4>Wedding <em>Catering</em></h4>
					<p>Sangeet, ceremony, reception. Custom menus crafted with your chef.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Explore Weddings →</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/corporate" class="related-link reveal delay-100">
					<p class="meta">Service · Corporate Catering</p>
					<h4>Corporate <em>Catering</em></h4>
					<p>Office lunches, conferences, holiday parties. On-time, every time.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Explore Corporate →</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/private-parties" class="related-link reveal delay-200">
					<p class="meta">Service · Private Parties</p>
					<h4>Private <em>Parties</em></h4>
					<p>Birthdays, anniversaries, housewarmings, holiday celebrations.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Explore Private →</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/cafe-catering" class="related-link reveal delay-300">
					<p class="meta">Service · Café Catering</p>
					<h4>Café &amp; <em>Chai</em></h4>
					<p>Live chai bars, specialty coffee, fresh-baked pastries.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Explore Café →</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="reveal">
			<p class="gold-label" style="color:var(--gold-light)">Ready When You Are</p>
			<h2>Let's Create<br/><em>Something Memorable</em></h2>
			<p>Tell us about your event. We'll respond within 24 hours.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/request-a-quote/" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
